{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I realized that I owe it-- I owe it to those people who died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I owe it to the people who perished, because if I don't talk about it, there are still idiots who are telling today that the Holocaust is a hoax, the same people who are telling you the earth is flat.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At least, that's my belief, including the geniuses, university professors, who tried to teach the world the Holocaust was a hoax.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if I don't stand up and if I-- we survivors don't talk, it may happen again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe we can stop it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe we can say it should never happen again anywhere, to any race, color, religion where a minority could be a scapegoat, because we were scapegoats.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- beyond any question that-- I mean, God has-- has a place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My question is what I'm doing today, that I think that I did, I continue to do and I will do it, to do the best possible Jewish education to my children, because that's the way my parents wanted it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the way I grew up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what-- that's the type of education that I was given.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, it's up to them to-- too go on the right road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To try to do anything possible that it should never be any kind of dictatorship of any dictator on Earth, and try to work on it that we should have freedom.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to anybody who doesn't know, they should read basically what is the-- one of the most beautiful document beside of religion is the American Bill of Rights.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe we can stop any dictator to have scapegoats again and kill people for no reason, no rhyme or reason.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
